# TextRepeatable - Protocol for text-like types that support repetition with an integer
module Core

### Defines the protocol `TextRepeatable`.
protocol TextRepeatable
  ### Returns the product of this value and the other value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$mul(you: Integral) -> Me
